  "body": "## What's Changed\r\n* Feature - podman volume export by @navidys in https://github.com/containers/podman-tui/pull/707\r\n* Feature - podman volume import by @navidys in https://github.com/containers/podman-tui/pull/708\r\n* Feature - adding UID and GID for volume create dialog by @navidys in https://github.com/containers/podman-tui/pull/709\r\n* Github action for auto draft release by @navidys in https://github.com/containers/podman-tui/pull/724\r\n* Packit for fedora downstream release by @navidys in https://github.com/containers/podman-tui/pull/725\r\n* Github action update go version by @navidys in https://github.com/containers/podman-tui/pull/726\r\n* Bump github.com/containers/podman/v5 from 5.7.1 to 5.8.0 by @dependabot[bot] in https://github.com/containers/podman-tui/pull/723\r\n* Bump github.com/sirupsen/logrus from 1.9.3 to 1.9.4 by @dependabot[bot] in https://github.com/containers/podman-tui/pull/715\r\n* Bump github.com/gdamore/tcell/v2 from 2.13.4 to 2.13.5 by @dependabot[bot] in https://github.com/containers/podman-tui/pull/706\r\n* Bump golang.org/x/crypto from 0.47.0 to 0.48.0 by @dependabot[bot] in https://github.com/containers/podman-tui/pull/722\r\n* Bump golang.org/x/crypto from 0.46.0 to 0.47.0 by @dependabot[bot] in https://github.com/containers/podman-tui/pull/713\r\n\r\n**Full Changelog**: https://github.com/containers/podman-tui/compare/v1.10.0...v1.11.0",
